message.content: Sannan ka shiga cikin shafin 'Settings' ta gida da kuma duba sauran ayyukan. Saka 'Accessibility' ko 'Inji' a cikin hanyar 'Settings'. Bayan haka, duba 'Vision' ko 'Bincike' a cikin sauran ayyukan. Saka 'Color Filters' ko 'Fulatoci na Launuka' domin samun fitar da zai kawo launuka. Bayan haka, saka 'Grayscale' ko 'Launin Fata' don shawarar fata, ko 'Color Tint' ko 'Launin Fata' don shawarar ta jima'i. Ka iya saita sauran fitattun launuka don samun launin fata ko jima'i da ke so.
